msgid ""
"KDE Menu Edit lets you edit how your apps are presented in application "
"launchers, such as Plasma's Application Launcher widget."
msgstr ""
"KDE Menua editatzeak aplikazio-abiarazleetan aplikazioak nola aurkezten "
"diren editatzen uzten dizu, Plasmaren aplikazio abiarazle trepetan esaterako."
